songs.title: I Want You Back (Live 2011)
songs.lyrics:
Oh baby, give me one more chance
(Show you that I love you)
Won't you please let me
Back in your heart?
Oh darlin', I was blind to let you go
(Let you go baby)
Now that I see you in her arms (I want you back)
I want you back (I want you back)
I want you back (I want you back)
Ooh ooh baby
I want you back (I want you back)
Ooh ooh ooh ooh
Oh baby, give me one more chance
(Show you that I love you)
Won't you please let me
Back in your heart
Oh darlin', I was blind to let you go (Let you go baby)
But now that I see you in her arms
I want you back
I want you back
Ooh ooh baby
